Views.name: V$_READ_LIST_FIRM
Views.Text: select distinct aa.id_firm, user_login, id_user, id_auth_user from ( select a01.id_firm, a01.user_login, a01.id_user, a01.id_auth_user from WM_AUTH_USER a01 where a01.is_use_current_firm = 1 union select d02.ID_COMPANY, a02.user_login, a02.id_user, a02.id_auth_user from WM_AUTH_USER a02, WM_LIST_R_HOLDING_COMPANY d02 where a02.IS_HOLDING = 1 and a02.ID_HOLDING = d02.ID_HOLDING union select b04.id_firm, a04.user_login, a04.id_user, a04.id_auth_user from WM_AUTH_USER a04, WM_LIST_COMPANY b04 where a04.is_root = 1 ) aa

Views.name: V$_READ_LIST_ROAD
Views.Text: select distinct aa.ID_HOLDING, aa.user_login, aa.id_user, aa.id_auth_user from ( select a01.ID_HOLDING, a01.user_login, a01.id_user, a01.id_auth_user from WM_AUTH_USER a01 where a01.IS_HOLDING = 1 union select b04.ID_HOLDING, a04.user_login, a04.id_user, a04.id_auth_user from WM_AUTH_USER a04, WM_LIST_HOLDING b04 where a04.is_root = 1 ) aa
